{"id": 1551, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你见过哪些新型“小题大做”？", "description": "时不时鼓足劲儿去隆重地做一件事，然后发现，咦？好像给自己加戏了。（题图来自：Ricardo Cavolo）", "record_count": 8389, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170306174829SWileLrRgbMzHh7q.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-06T17:00:34Z", "questions": [{"id": 2009, "title": "现如今，你见过哪些新型“小题大做”？", "content": "你在什么事情上控制不住地“小题大做”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 175276, "content": "认真理财：存不下钱来，但研究各种理财方式", "image": "img/option/option/20170306175944dbG2iH9ZUTRzpvXW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175292, "content": "生活精致：知道店家会修图，拍证件照还是坚持化底妆", "image": "img/option/option/20170306180005mXi9upNPDCH3gR0K.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175308, "content": "为人谦逊：知乎上被人邀请回答问题，要庄重地回复一句谢邀", "image": "img/option/option/2017030618005081Gp2ZyRHYxhTI4a.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175310, "content": "准备充分：为一个面试，看了几百套脑筋急转弯", "image": "img/option/option/20170306180625kVyIgjKmDxOClSL1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175316, "content": "爱岗敬业：新进公司，年会每一个节目恨不得都发一个小视频", "image": "img/option/option/20170306180238Nk9y6nQ7YCvEje3x.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175317, "content": "磨刀不误砍柴工：烘焙，买工具花了大几千就做了两回", "image": "img/option/option/20170306181555OJfkQ3FyEputjnbH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175323, "content": "爱惜身体：感冒咳嗽三天就觉得自己得了绝症，做个全套检查", "image": "img/option/option/20170306181242QoXKTSxb0h1arMnj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 175390, "content": "过分认真：花好几天编辑豆瓣自我介绍，尽管被0人关注", "image": "img/option/option/20170306224311fiBZG1XEymuhtrkJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}